{
  "texts": [
    "Given that the gains our model achieves in IoU and F1score are more significant than its minor deficit in APLS, our proposed architecture offers the most compelling and well-balanced performance profile.",
    "We therefore select the 'mmmm-aaaa' configuration as our final design.",
    "Necessity of the SSM Component.",
    "To verify the importance of Mamba's core SSM mechanism, especially in light of recent work questioning its necessity for all vision tasks [43], we replaced the SSM component in the VSS blocks with a simple identity mapping.",
    "As shown in Table 6, removing the SSM from any part of the network leads to a significant drop in performance."
  ]
}